				</div>			
			</div>	
		</div>  
		<div class="container-fluid donation_card_enlarge">	
			<div class="row" style="">
				<div class="col-sm-6">	
					<div class="donation_card_enlarge_img"></div>	
					<div class="donation_card_enlarge_title">兩岸菁英學生交流計畫</div>
